{"tid":1193428,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 說出 iOS 13／iPadOS 支援滑鼠的原因！不是給正常人用的！","createTime":"2019-06-09T02:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T03:28:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e006dffba84d2332e3c9ad7f9908413ecd397b2","tid":1193428,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"編輯部昨天測試 iPad Pro 配合 iPadOS 時發現，iPadOS 竟然可以使用滑鼠！對於 iOS 13 /iPadOS 上可用 USB/Bluetooth Mouse，人們都感到興奮，認為 Apple 是為了讓 iPad 更像 PC 能進行更精細的動作而設，例如修圖。不過這滑鼠的「游標」十分醜，實在難以想像是出自重視設計的 Apple 之手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mouse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fmouse.jpg&h=f6b092f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科技記者 Steven Aquino 在 Twitter 上表示，從他的消息得知，支援滑鼠其實是「輔助使用」功能(AssistiveTouch 選單內），Apple 留給傷殘人士使用的功能。<br />\n<br />\n那就是說，留給一些無法以手觸控螢幕，只能用滑鼠或 Joystick 的人使用 。對於健全的人士，這功能的相信不是留給大家作為傳統滑鼠之用。"},{"pid":"ef11fd69f430e9db176664860c29d6165ad9527b","tid":1193428,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/05/ios13-ipados-support-mouse-reason/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2Fios13-ipados-support-mouse-reason%2F&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHRhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=1e361dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/05/ios13-ipados-support-mouse-reason/</a>"},{"pid":"b484337349f85c5359a545f114f009e66a299c7d","tid":1193428,"uid":20449,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a046d86895ff9024e049d9b7995cb67091762b45","tid":1193428,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"對於 iOS 13 /iPadOS 上可用 USB/Bluetooth Mouse，人們都感到興奮<img src=\"/assets/face